Package: TreeSwitchR
Type: Package
Title: TreeSwitchR visualize phylogenetic trees along chromosomes in R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Kristian K",
           family = "Ullrich",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "ullrich@evolbio.mpg.de",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4308-9626"))
Description: TreeSwitchR visualize phylogenetic trees along chromosomes in R.
    Given a tree file and the corresponding genomic positions, trees are
    visualized and compared to their corresponding neighbors. Tree topology
    switches as well as their underlying genomic features are highlighted.
